title: Duck in Water
description: A duck swimming in calm water. The duck has a brown body with a distinctive white head and a blue bill.

title: Biodiversity Map
description: An illustrated map showcasing the biodiversity of a region, featuring various animals such as birds, a turtle, and amphibians around the edges. The map itself highlights geographical features with green and blue tones, indicating land and water areas.

title: Map with Wildlife Illustrations
description: The image features a stylized map of a region, showcasing various waterways and topographical details. Surrounding the map are illustrations of wildlife, including a turtle in water, a salamander, and a bird of prey, highlighting the area's biodiversity.

title: Map with Birds
description: An illustrated map featuring various shades of green representing land and water bodies. The map includes blue lines indicating rivers and streams, with pink outlines marking specific areas. Surrounding the map are illustrations of different bird species, adding a natural element to the geographic representation.

title: Bird Walking in Water
description: A bird with a black and white plumage is walking through shallow water. The background features a warm, golden hue, suggesting a sunset or sunrise, which reflects on the water's surface.

title: Great Egret in Water
description: A great egret stands gracefully in shallow water, its long neck extended and beak pointed forward. The bird's white feathers contrast beautifully with the blue water, reflecting its image. The background is softly blurred, enhancing the focus on the egret.

title: Golden Grass
description: A close-up view of tall grass with golden and green hues, swaying gently in the breeze. The grass appears vibrant and lush, with fine strands creating a textured appearance.
